sub_title: Water Modelling || Climate Adaptation || Sustainable Energy || Project Management
summary: Hi, this is Faysal, I am currently Interning at PWNT as a part of my second Master's degree in Urban Environmental Management at Wageningen University and Research. I formerly worked for a British non-profit organisation for three years as a Project Officer, where my primary responsibilities were field coordinating, community engagement, stakeholders management and assisting with project management. My accomplishments include documentation and reporting, grand winning, strategy creation and development for various initiatives (including plans and tools), and capacity building. I am especially knowledgeable about sustainable water supply and treatment technologies, sustainable energy and project management. I am especially interested in climate induced water challenges and advancement in automation through advance environmental modelling. I constantly push my boundaries in order to achieve new heights and to have a positive and expansive mindset in order to "Make The Difference.‚Äù
